# .design/ — design source + Figma tooling.
# COMMITTED: scripts/ + the WHOLE figma-cache/ — config/manifest/index/frames AND assets/.
#   The cache (incl. page renders / image references) is the offline source of truth for
#   pixel-perfect work, so a fresh checkout / CI has every visual reference with no token
#   and no quota. .design/ is dev-only (never served; excluded from the Docker image),
#   so none of this ships to prod (Principle II is about public/, not .design/). See ADR 0010.

# Master Figma export + raw source imports (the .fig + image dump) — redundant with the cloud file.
images/

# Throwaway verification screenshots (charlotte), EXCEPT the tracked cache renders under assets/.
*.png
!figma-cache/assets/
!figma-cache/assets/**
